Class Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • Container
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContainerInterface

    public class Container
extends java.lang.Object
implements ContainerInterface
    Container class contains a stack of DonationPackage and simulates adding and removing package from the container’s stack.

    Alex Juan
